hotspot2 0, -B / 2, unID : unID = unID + 1 hotspot2 A, -B / 2, unID : unID = unID + 1 hotspot2 A, B / 2, unID : unID = unID + 1 hotspot2 0, B / 2, unID : unID = unID + 1

Symbol.Script_1D:
dim aDefaultLength[4] aDefaultLength[1] = 2.23 aDefaultLength[2] = 3.33 aDefaultLength[3] = 5.19 aDefaultLength[4] = 6.34
legLength = sqr((B / 2)^2 + ZZYZX^2) legAngle = atn(B / 2 / ZZYZX) legTilt = 10 legOffset = ZZYZX * tan(legTilt)
beamThk = 0.1 beamLength = legLength * 0.95
spikeLength = legLength * 0.2 spikeThk = beamThk * 0.9 spikeGroove = spikeThk / 4
plateThk = 0.01 plateHeight = 0.25 plateTrim = 0.02
crossBeamRad = 0.05 crossBeamOffset = 0.15
seatWidth = 0.6 seatDepth = 0.2 seatThk = 0.02 seatRad = seatDepth / 2 seatBend = 1 seatHeight = 0.5 seatOffset = 0.7
babySeatWidth = 0.30 babySeatDepth = 0.25 babySeatHeight = babySeatDepth babySeatRad = 0.08 babySeatThk = 0.002
connectionWidth = seatWidth * 1.2 ropeRad = 0.006
if nSeats < 3 then nLegs = 2 else nLegs = 3 endif
dim aCrossBeamSegments[2] if nLegs = 2 then aCrossBeamSegments[1] = A - legOffset * 2 - beamThk aCrossBeamSegments[2] = 0 else if nSeats = 3 then aCrossBeamSegments[1] = (A - legOffset * 2 - beamThk * 2) / 3 aCrossBeamSegments[2] = aCrossBeamSegments[1] * 2 else aCrossBeamSegments[1] = (A - legOffset * 2 - beamThk * 2) / 2 aCrossBeamSegments[2] = aCrossBeamSegments[1] endif endif
dim aSeatPositions[4] aSeatPositions[1] = 0 aSeatPositions[2] = 0 aSeatPositions[3] = 0 aSeatPositions[4] = 0
if nSeats = 1 then aSeatPositions[1] = A / 2 endif
if nSeats = 2 then aSeatPositions[1] = legOffset + seatOffset aSeatPositions[2] = A - legOffset - seatOffset endif
if nSeats = 3 then aSeatPositions[1] = legOffset + aCrossBeamSegments[1] / 2 aSeatPositions[2] = legOffset + aCrossBeamSegments[1] + seatOffset + beamThk aSeatPositions[3] = A - seatOffset - legOffset endif
if nSeats = 4 then aSeatPositions[1] = legOffset + seatOffset aSeatPositions[2] = A / 2 - seatOffset - beamThk aSeatPositions[3] = A / 2 + seatOffset + beamThk aSeatPositions[4] = A - legOffset - seatOffset endif
dim bBabySeats[4] bBabySeats[1] = 0 bBabySeats[2] = 0 bBabySeats[3] = 0 bBabySeats[4] = 0
if bBabySeat then if nSeats < 4 then bBabySeats[1] = 1 else bBabySeats[1] = 1 bBabySeats[2] = 1 endif endif
